{"url":"http://www.miyazaki-group.com/recruiting/staff/04.html","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n<head>\n<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->\n<script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-G41M5YF4VE\"></script>\n<script>\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n  gtag('js', new Date());\n\n  gtag('config', 'G-G41M5YF4VE');\n</script>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <title>STAFF04 | 株式会社宮崎商店</title>\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"岩手の地元に密着70年。宮崎商店のホームページようこそ。\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no\">\n  <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/assets/css/style.min.css\">\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins:400,600,700\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n</head>\n<body class=\"\">\n  <div class=\"l-wrapper l-header__overlay\">\n\n    <header class=\"l-header\">\n      <div class=\"l-header__inner\">\n        <div class=\"l-header__head\">\n          <p class=\"l-header__logo\">\n            <a href=\"/\">\n              <img src=\"/assets/images/common/logo_corp_header.png\" alt=\"宮崎商店\">\n            </a>\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"l-header__nav-icon js-gnav-toggle\">\n            <span></span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <nav class=\"l-header__body js-gnav-list\">\n          <ul class=\"l-header__list\">\n            <li class=\"l-header__item\">\n              <a class=\"l-header__link l-header__link--01\" href=\"/recruiting/\">リクルーティング</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"l-header__item\">\n              <a class=\"l-header__link l-header__link--02\" href=\"/business/\">事業案内</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"l-header__item\">\n              <a class=\"l-header__link l-header__link--03\" href=\"/company/\">会社案内</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"l-header__item\">\n              <a class=\"l-header__link l-header__link--04\" href=\"https://www.talent-clip.jp/miyazaki-group/\" target=\"_blank\">採用情報</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"l-header__item\">\n              <a class=\"l-header__link l-header__link--05\" href=\"/contact/\">お問い合わせ</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"l-header__item l-header-sub\">\n              <span class=\"l-header__link l-header__link--fb js-fb-toggle\">Facebook</span>\n              <ul class=\"l-header-sub__list\">\n                <li class=\"l-header-sub__item\">\n                  <a class=\"l-header-sub__link\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E5%AE%AE%E5%B4%8E%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97-2062845797276368/\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook 宮崎商店</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"l-header-sub__item\">\n                  <a class=\"l-header-sub__link\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/spasentoyukkomorioka/\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook ゆっこ盛岡</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"l-header-sub__item is-no-link\">\n                  <a class=\"l-header-sub__link\">COMING SOON !</a>\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </nav>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n\n\n    <section class=\"l-main\">\n\n      <div class=\"c-breadcrumb\">\n        <div class=\"c-inner\">\n          <ul class=\"c-breadcrumb__list\">\n            <li class=\"c-breadcrumb__item\"><a href=\"/\">HOME</a></li>\n            <li class=\"c-breadcrumb__item\"><a href=\"/recruiting/\">リクルーティング</a></li>\n            <li class=\"c-breadcrumb__item\">STAFF04</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"l-contents u-pt-0\">\n        <div class=\"p-staff p-staff--04\">\n          <div class=\"p-staff__inner\">\n\n            <section class=\"p-staff__box\">\n\n              <p class=\"p-staff__department p-staff__department--mirai-energy\">\n                <span class=\"p-staff__department__en\">HOME ENERGY</span>\n                <br class=\"pc-hidden\"><span class=\"p-staff__department__jp\">ホームエネルギー事業</span>\n              </p>\n\n              <div class=\"c-hdg-lv1 p-staff__ttl\">\n                <h1 class=\"c-hdg-lv1__txt\">見えないところにこそ、美学がある。</h1>\n              </div>\n\n\n              <section class=\"p-staff__paragraph\">\n                <div class=\"c-hdg-lv2 c-hdg-lv2--simple\">\n                  <h2 class=\"c-hdg-lv2__txt\">身につけた技術で勝負できる世界</h2>\n                </div>\n\n                <p>私の仕事は、主にエアコンの設置や撤去。以前は会場設営の仕事をしていましたが、ここで働く先輩から「自分の腕をいかす仕事」と聞いて興味を持ち、転職しました。未経験からスタートして６年。先輩たちをお手本に、現場で経験を積みながら仕事を覚えていきました。特に好きな作業は溶接。溶接の跡を見ればその人の腕がだいたいわかるんですよ。表には見えない部分だけど、仕上がりにこだわる。そんなところに「職人の美学」を感じます。</p>\n              </section>\n\n\n              <section class=\"p-staff__paragraph\">\n                <div class=\"c-hdg-lv2 c-hdg-lv2--simple\">\n                  <h2 class=\"c-hdg-lv2__txt\">失敗から学べることがたくさんある</h2>\n                </div>\n\n                <p>失敗は、自分の足りないところを知り成長できるいい機会。私もいろんな失敗をしましたが、周りがフォローしてくれたので、失敗を恐れず技術を身につけることができたと思っています。これからも先輩たちの背中を追いかけながら、誰にも負けないスキルを磨いていきたいです。</p>\n              </section>\n\n\n              <p class=\"p-staff__paragraph\">\n                <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/staff/04/img_01.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n              </p>\n\n              <div class=\"p-staff__data\">\n                <div class=\"p-staff-data\">\n                  <h2 class=\"p-staff-data__ttl\">DATA</h2>\n                  <div class=\"p-staff-data__right\">\n                    <p class=\"p-staff-data__name\">◎グループ会社 （株）ユートー・工事部<br>荒澤 雄大  盛岡大学文学部 卒</p>\n                    <p class=\"p-staff-data__career\">北海道出身。2011年入社。幼少時からアイスホッケーを始め、現在も社会人チームで活動。審判の資格も所持しており、2016年のいわて国体冬季大会で審判を務めた。</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </section>\n          </div><!-- /.p-staff__inner -->\n\n\n          <div class=\"p-staff-nav\">\n            <nav class=\"p-staff-nav__inner\">\n              <ul class=\"p-staff-nav__list\">\n                <li class=\"p-staff-nav__item\">\n                  <a class=\"p-staff-nav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/01.html\">\n                    <div class=\"p-staff-nav__icon\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/staff/common/icon_nav_01.png\" alt=\"\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-staff-nav__txt\">\n                      <p class=\"p-staff-nav__stars\">MIYAZAKI RISING STARS!</p>\n                      <p class=\"p-staff-nav__num\">#001</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"p-staff-nav__item\">\n                  <a class=\"p-staff-nav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/02.html\">\n                    <div class=\"p-staff-nav__icon\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/staff/common/icon_nav_02.png\" alt=\"\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-staff-nav__txt\">\n                      <p class=\"p-staff-nav__stars\">MIYAZAKI RISING STARS!</p>\n                      <p class=\"p-staff-nav__num\">#002</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"p-staff-nav__item\">\n                  <a class=\"p-staff-nav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/03.html\">\n                    <div class=\"p-staff-nav__icon\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/staff/common/icon_nav_03.png\" alt=\"\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-staff-nav__txt\">\n                      <p class=\"p-staff-nav__stars\">MIYAZAKI RISING STARS!</p>\n                      <p class=\"p-staff-nav__num\">#003</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"p-staff-nav__item\">\n                  <a class=\"p-staff-nav__link is-staff-current\">\n                    <div class=\"p-staff-nav__icon\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/staff/common/icon_nav_04.png\" alt=\"\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-staff-nav__txt\">\n                      <p class=\"p-staff-nav__stars\">MIYAZAKI RISING STARS!</p>\n                      <p class=\"p-staff-nav__num\">#004</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"p-staff-nav__item\">\n                  <a class=\"p-staff-nav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/05.html\">\n                    <div class=\"p-staff-nav__icon\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/staff/common/icon_nav_05.png\" alt=\"\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-staff-nav__txt\">\n                      <p class=\"p-staff-nav__stars\">MIYAZAKI RISING STARS!</p>\n                      <p class=\"p-staff-nav__num\">#005</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </a>\n                </li>\n                <!--li class=\"p-staff-nav__item\">\n                  <a class=\"p-staff-nav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/06.html\">\n                    <div class=\"p-staff-nav__icon\">\n                      <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/staff/common/icon_nav_06.png\" alt=\"\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"p-staff-nav__txt\">\n                      <p class=\"p-staff-nav__stars\">MIYAZAKI RISING STARS!</p>\n                      <p class=\"p-staff-nav__num\">#006</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </a>\n                </li-->\n              </ul>\n            </nav>\n          </div>\n\n\n        </div><!-- /.p-staff -->\n      </div>\n\n    </section><!-- /.l-main -->\n    <style>\n      @media screen and (min-width: 769px) {\n        .p-staff-nav__list {\n          justify-content: flex-start;\n        }\n        .p-staff-nav__item {\n          margin-right: 12px;\n        }\n        .p-staff-nav__item:nth-child(3n) {\n          margin-right: 0;\n        }\n      }\n    </style>\n\n    <footer class=\"l-footer\">\n      <div class=\"l-footer__links\">\n        <p class=\"l-footer-links__corporate-logo\">\n          <a href=\"/\">\n            <img src=\"/assets/images/common/logo_corp_footer.png\" alt=\"宮崎商店 Miyazaki Syoten Ltd.\">\n          </a>\n        </p>\n        <nav class=\"l-footer-links__nav\">\n          <ul class=\"l-footer-links__list\">\n            <li class=\"l-footer-links__item\">\n              <a href=\"/privacy/\">個人情報保護方針</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"l-footer-links__item\">\n              <a href=\"/sitemap.html\">サイトマップ</a>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </nav>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"l-footer__copyright\">\n        <p>\n          Copyright 2017(c) Miyazaki Syoten Co.,Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </footer>\n\n\n  </div><!-- /.l-wrapper -->\n\n  <script src=\"/assets/js/jquery-3.1.1.min.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"/assets/js/jquery.easing.1.3.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"/assets/js/slick.min.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"/assets/js/jquery.fadethis.min.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"/assets/js/common.js\"></script>\n\n</body>\n</html>","finalUrl":"http://www.miyazaki-group.com/recruiting/staff/04.html","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-24T00:01:33.429Z"}